description:
Welcome to JimLiElevators: My name is Jim and I am an elevator photographer based in central Texas. I have always loved elevators when I was a kid. Been filming since 2005. I present to you videos of elevators that are both vintage and modern. Not only that I film elevators, but I've also been interested into trains as well. I'll occasionally upload animated elevators because I've had a lot of fun making them. So with that said, I hope you enjoy your visit to my channel.

Thanks so much for your loyal viewership. I take pride in keeping this channel clean for all ages. I am also a born Christian, so I want to keep it pleasing to Jesus as well! “For God so loved the world that he gave his only son that believes in him shall not perish but have eternal life. John 3:16."

I'm also thankful to Andrew Reams (DieselDucy) who's the deepest inspiration towards me to start this channel. That said, make sure you subscribe. Thanks and have a great day! :D

description:
「ぼくたちにとって動いて見えるテレビ映像ですら、昆虫から見ればカタカタとした 動きにしか見えない。時間とはいったい何だろうか？」
時間を引きのばして昆虫の世界を見れば、そこには驚異の世界が見えてくる。私たちがスムーズに見えるテレビもカマキリが見たらコマ落としの映像にしかみえないだろう。（なにしろ獲物を捕る速度はわずか1/20秒である）
それほど昆虫の動きは早い。普通のビデオカメラではとらえきれない昆虫の動きや行動を高速度ビデオカメラを用いて時間を10倍から40倍に引き延ばして撮影している。
今では動画はビデオカメラだけでなくスチールカメラでも撮れる。このコーナーでは撮りだめた数々の動画や新しくスチールカメラで撮っている最新動画などを掲載していくことにする。

description:
I make videos of trains mainly in Ohio, Kentucky, Indiana, Pennsylvania, Florida and West Virginia.  My specialty has been the Peavine Line also known as the Cincinnati Line.  This line runs from Clare Yard in Mariemont Ohio MP 9 to Portsmouth Ohio about MP 105.  However, no trains have gone past MP 78 since 2003.  This Peavine Line is in operation from MP 9 to MP 78.445 at Plum Run Ohio.  The last train past MP 78.445 was 2003.  Also, the line had been closed for almost 11 months past MP 32.84 .  I have videos of the last and first trains from those dates.  Currently this line has 2 customers: Huhtamaki at MP 30 and Winchester Ag. at MP 57.5 but the line is also used for car storage.  Winchester Ag shipped 26 loads in 2012 and about 97 in 2013.  In 2014, they only shipped January to April.  Venmo & Cash App - @Jawtooth

Aimed Research is currently the most affordable high-speed imaging solution in America, utilizing top-tier cameras and flash units for research, development and engineering. Aimed Research's knowledge-base and skills were acquired directly from the defense industry and we therefore provide specialized services for ballistic tests. Our cameras and flash units are available for rental to select customers or with an operator for on-site service to any customer. 

Aimed Research is supported by professional talent that has designed programmable munitions, firing control systems and other electronics, though Aimed Research is not currently a manufacturer of any products. Aimed Research is open to work in-part or in-whole with your organization to provide accelerated results for your product development.

description:
Daniel Sanchez is a Texas born Motorcycle Builder, Automotive, Residential and Commercial Fabricator with more than 20 years experience in his field. Inspiration for his work comes from a family history of metal workers, including his Great Grandfather who was an Apache Metal Artisan. The style and originality showcased in CTC motorcycles is indicative of his diverse heritage stemming from Mexican, Apache Indian and American roots.
​
More widely known as a motorcycle builder, he does much more than that. Custom projects have ranged from Oil & Gas Wellhead Guards to small home fences and even show trophies.
​
Cut Throat Customs is conveniently located on the outskirts of Houston in Humble, TX

Specializing in 

Motorcycle Parts - Custom Car, Truck & Bike Builds

Precinct is the new game from Jim Walls, creator of the original Police Quest series from Sierra.  Precinct takes place in the corrupt town of Fraser Canyon. Players begin the game as rookie police officer Maxwell Jones, and quickly learn just how corrupt and dangerous Fraser Canyon really is. 

Each day of the Kickstarter campaign will feature a brand new exclusive video in this section! Check back daily for a new bit of history you've never heard before, including; visits to the old Sierra buildings in Oakhurst, a visit Ken and Roberta's old house, and several fascinating stories from Robert and Jim as they reminisce about the old days at Sierra.

We are funding development of the game entirely through our Kickstarter campaign.  To find out more about the game and our Kickstarter campaign, click the link inside any video.

description:
The ISU Multiphase Flow Laboratory is a research lab at Iowa State University in the Mechanical Engineering Department. The lab does research with cold flow fluidized beds, bubble columns, screw pyrolizers, and stirred tank reactors. The custom built X-ray vault found within the lab allows for the visualization of fluid flows in opaque systems. 
A video introduction to the lab and equipment can be found on the College of Engineering Youtube channel and is linked below.
This lab is run by Ted Heindel, Bergles Professor of Themal Science at Iowa State University.

description:
NASA's mission is to pioneer the future in space exploration, scientific discovery and aeronautics research. To do that, thousands of people have been working around the world and in space for more than 50 years, trying to answer some basic questions. What's out there in space? How do we get there? What will we find? What can we learn there -- or learn just by trying to get there -- that will make life better here on Earth?

NASA's work is diverse: proving flight technologies; creating capabilities for sustainable human and robotic exploration; exploring Earth, the solar system and the universe beyond; developing critical enabling technologies such as the space shuttle; and conducting science in orbit aboard the International Space Station. With NASA you can explore the universe and discover Earth.

Texashighdef was founded and managed in 2008 by my uncle. Sadly, he passed away unexpectedly in July 2023. While his legal name was Lindsay, he was affectionately known as Duke to his friends and family. He entrusted me, his niece and namesake, with continuing the legacy of this channel. I am dedicated to preserving and enhancing Texashighdef’s tradition of providing calming and relaxing content, as he has done for the past 15 years. As I am still relatively new to this role, I would greatly appreciate any feedback and suggestions. 

Much love, Lindsay O’Connor.

Thanks for stopping by.
Duke

description:
Olá, sou Fabrício Rabachim, profissional autodidata em Efeitos Visuais (VFX), trabalho há mais de 15 anos com computação gráfica, tanto na publicidade, quanto no cinema.

Criado em 2005, com o intuito de postar meus estudos, testes e trabalhos do audiovisual, esse canal foi crescendo e já serviu como repositório de tutoriais de efeitos visuais do antigo site VFX do Fabrício.

Hoje, além de continuar postando projetos, estudos e eventuais tutoriais, o canal é a moradia de alguns dos meus animais de estimação favoritos, como o famoso Tuba, nosso baby shark brasileiro com fama internacional. Esse filhote de tubarão animado já foi parar na TV e dá o que falar pela internet afora. Também temos algumas simpáticas aranhas, além de eventuais cenas inusitadas com outros animais e insetos variados.

Ahhh... e meus curtas metragens e trabalhos mais elaborados em computação gráfica, também fazem parte do cardápio ;)

CONTATO COMERCIAL: fabriciovfx.yt@gmail.com

Hey, I’m Lena Miculek – welcome to my world! 🎯💥 

I’m taking over this channel from my dad, Jerry Miculek – one of the greatest shooters of all time – and bringing you into the next chapter of our story. This is where pro-level shooting meets everyday joy, ridiculous challenges, inspiring stories, and a whole lot of fun. It’s all about community and building our Trigger Tribe – where everyone is welcome, encouraged, and inspired to grow, play, and laugh with us. 

You’ll find: 
🎯 My life as a pro shooter (and proud goofball) 
🔥 Behind-the-scenes training & world-level competitions 
❤️ Inspiring stories & wild challenges 
💡 Firearms education with heart 
🎥 Vlogs with family, friends & Trigger Tribe guests. 

The range can be more than targets — it can be a place of confidence, connection, and belonging. That’s the world I want to build. Welcome to the Trigger Tribe. Let’s do this together!

For more than 50 years, Santana has sold over 100 million records and has performed for three generations of concert fans worldwide. To date, Santana has won 10 GRAMMY Awards and three Latin Grammys. He won a record-tying nine Grammys for a single project for 1999’s Supernatural (including Album of the Year and Record of the Year for “Smooth”) as well as three Latin Grammys. He has also received the Billboard Century Award (1996), was ushered into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame (1998), received the Billboard Latin Music Awards’ Lifetime Achievement honor (2009), and was the recipient of the Kennedy Center Honors Award (2013). Among many other honors, Carlos Santana has been cited by Rolling Stone as #15 on their list of the “100 Greatest Guitarists of All Time.”
His forthcoming album Africa Speaks will be released on June 7, 2019.

This scientific youtube channel presents our research and documents the progress in the field of optical surface metrology. It shows highspeed projection techniques for stereophotogrammetry setups with structured light. This allows highspeed 3D shape acquisition of humans/faces or fast moving objects while inspection.

Since January 2014, we are granted the EXIST-Gründerstipendium from the Federal Ministry for Economic Affairs and Energy (BMWi) for transferring the Highspeed 3D Metrology Technologies into the University Spin-Off EnShape

We hope you enjoy our videos, visit the hompages and come back soon.

Workgroup 3D-Metrology and EnShape GmbH

description:
EDM- Electric Discharge Machining is a machining process that uses a series of electric discharges (sparks) to erode material from a work piece.
Wire EDM, Sinker EDM, Grinding EDM and Hole Drilling EDM are products manufactured by NOVICK®. Electrical Discharge Machining can be used to machine any electrical conductive materials of any hardness to an accuracy of up to one-thousandth of a millimeter with no mechanical action. By virtue of these properties, EDM is key technology in the manufacture of high-performance molds, press tools for the series production of plastic, glass and metal parts, and for the direct machining of complex mechanical precision components.

Vybz Kartel's official VEVO channel.

Adidja Azim Palmer (born 7 January 1976) better known as Vybz Kartel, is a Jamaican musical artist, record producer, entrepreneur and dancehall performer. Among his various nicknames, he is referred to as "Worl' Boss" and has been recognised as one of the genre’s most prolific and skilled lyricists credited with further popularising dancehall. Kartel's singles have achieved cultural ubiquity across the Caribbean, including "Ramping Shop" (2009), "Summer Time" and "Dancehall Hero" (2013). Having collaborated with a number of internationally prominent hip hop and R&B artists such as Major Lazer, Rihanna and Jay Z, he has also been credited as an inspiration for the dancehall-infused work of a number of Western artists, including Drake, who has cited Kartel as being one of his "biggest inspirations".

description:
Hello, i am Stella Stig and i have been gaming for around 20+ years, starting off with the mighty playstation 1 back when it first came out, the original Gran Turismo was the first driving game i played and since then i have progressed onto the xbox, first with the original xbox, then the 360 and now the xbox one and also PC.

I am an avid Forza Fan and have enjoyed all the forza games, with Forza 2 being my favourite. I also play a host of games on pc, including Arma 2, R Factor and the odd Sim Game.

I try to make my videos as entertaining and informative as possible and i hope you all enjoy them. Thank you all for the support you have shown me and i look forward to entertaining you guys more.

Stella

Also to go to my twitch channel for info on all my dates for my live streams: www.twitch.tv/stellastiglive

description: Priolite ist einer der jüngsten Blitzgeräte-Hersteller auf dem europäischen Markt und entwickelt seit 2009 innovative Produkte für professionelle Anwender. Das deutsche Unternehmen mit Sitz im Würzburg wurde von Dipl.-Ing. Joachim Renschke gegründet und kombiniert modernste Technologien zu einem einzigartigen Lichtsystem für den modernen Fotografen von heute: LED für hocheffiziente Energienutzung. Li-Ionen-Akkus für mobilen Einsatz bei reduziertem Gewicht. Bidirektionale Funktechnik für höchsten Komfort. Power Factor Correction (PFC) für kürzeste Ladezeit im weltweiten Stromnetz. Hot Sync für mobiles Blitzen bis 1/8000 Sekunde Verschlusszeit bei voller Lichtleistung. Priolite garantiert führende Blitztechnik - unter strenger Qualitätskontrolle designed, entwickelt und gefertigt in Deutschland.

-WATWAREHD: A Diverse Railfan:  Railfanning North East.-

Hello, welcome to my channel.  Here you will find some of the best CSX, Norfolk Southern, NYSW, and NJ Transit videos on YouTube.  I am a very diverse railfan so don't expect just those four railroads. Here at WATWARE Productions we make railfanning like you are actually there.

Please check out my subscribers', subscriptions, and recommended  videos and channels.  Only the best of the best are on there.

 I also have an O-Scale Layout.  I am going to get an expansion with Lionel Fastrak.  The layout is going to be based on Conrail, NJT, and NYSW in the 90s.  So, if you like roaring freights, 80 m.p.h. passenger trains, and O-Scale trains, SUBSCRIBE!

My Equipment:

Primary Camera:  Sony HDR CX-160

Secondary Cameras:  GoPro HD Hero2, Samsung SMX F43BN, Flip UltraHD

Tripod: Sunpak 7500TM Tripod/Monopod

I WILL NOT TOLERATE ANY NEGATIVE COMMENTS!!!
